Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,02
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不到人的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽不到聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也…見不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是「不在」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良不在 衛不在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.53,0:02:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士不在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.15,0:02:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道生不在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多很多人都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我卻還在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎和真矢都想戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北極…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是可能有去無回的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也再沒有其他選擇了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泥土
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和祝福者的身體一樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:36.51,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(520,80)}Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把大家 把總士…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奪走的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還…從來沒見過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然會碰我的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…你不是在Alvis嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來拿換洗的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有…來看看你的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 我的身體 還能動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在變得和咲良一樣之前 我還有時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎 法芙娜你已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士說了 我們可能要參加人類軍的作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們做的用來打倒祝福者的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能已經超乎你們的想像 成為了我們的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說傻話 所以就要讓我批准你們參加人類軍魯莽的決戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 只有這個辦法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸你自己失去媽媽的時候肯定也是這樣的心情吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 你沒有打倒敵人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我有！有法芙娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我養大就是為了對付他們的吧！爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住嘴！不許再說這種話！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說 如果把你和Mk.Sein投入決戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.07,0:05:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼保護島
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有遠見和卡農
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還有劍司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們…會保護島的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你憑什麼保證連逃離前線的人都會再開法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍司還剩下什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良和衛都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連他媽媽也不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在他還有什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過不了多久他就會自己提出要開了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼…蠢話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己也明白的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該明白吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我去啊 爸爸！求你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁我現在還動得了 趁我還沒變成咲良那樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一個人去北極
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體越來越遲鈍了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛也很快要看不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會變得什麼也想不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很快就會…活著變成另一種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就要不在了啊 爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見醫生很快就會找到救你們的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼來得及！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.81,0:06:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁我還是我的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我去戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 讓我去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我一個人去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:06:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是決定島要怎樣作戰的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸你是現在這個島上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一一個會命令我們去戰鬥的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是嗎…爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會送走你們 送走所有想要戰鬥的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到島的復原工作結束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後 我會準備送你去北極
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手上的泥巴洗乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等乾掉 就弄不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好寂寞的風
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到最近 整個島上還都開滿了花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在樹 花和蟲子卻都死了 只剩下寂靜的風
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的浪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為島缺了一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整個島的周圍都是那麼大的浪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是唯獨我的身邊 卻是毫無起伏的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要開上法芙娜 悲傷和寂寞的感覺都會從心裡消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子離開的時候 是不是也是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為太想消除悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然這麼想開法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不在了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和祝福者有什麼區別呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…和祝福者有什麼區別呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家裡一團亂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家 我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廚房 客廳 餐桌 浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都像是陌生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽的房間 工作的用品全都掉在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:11:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽要是看到了會生氣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平的地方 安全又溫暖的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到頭來 這才是我最珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 它們全都失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.96,0:11:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 衛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良 陪著我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來個人 陪著我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 已經沒有任何地方待得下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子 還是第一次那樣求我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從他很小的時候開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就從來沒有那樣過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把他送到去了就回不來的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外 我就沒有其他辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅音…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,03
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家尋求著希望 卻走向與之不同的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的答案 才剛剛覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點 快來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回到島上來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否則會就這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡農 對不起 我來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 該道歉的是我 要你陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說要想駕駛神劍型 就要和別人一起訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為瞭解彼此的心 對於駕駛我們的法芙娜是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐間老師在做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.16,0:13:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進去了之後要去找到對方 這個你有聽說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 雖然不知道要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我會試試的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會想辦法去找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是一團迷霧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人也看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平穩的水面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的那一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,映著我的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 還映著很多其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一騎 卡農 近藤 還有大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子也在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日井 咲良 還有小楯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島上的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 姐姐 道生哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊有爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像都在鏡子的裡面一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像在外面的我才是被關起來的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面…有光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火 像手掌那麼大的火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃燒著 落了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅得刺眼 又漂亮的火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 火往霧的那邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在叫我過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗的海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我站在沉了一半的船上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:17:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鮮紅的木材造出的老舊的船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船頭亮著光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴比倫 我那已經不動的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這艘船嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正乘著壞掉的船 在黑暗的海上徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讓人生厭的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些 會被真矢看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海的上面出現了火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡也有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一大團紅色的火…越變越大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡的火…有一團靠過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:19:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…這團火是…道生…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霧漸漸散了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壯觀…好多的火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你嗎 道生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算爬上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真 真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 卡農你果然在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成你…你爬上來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因為到處都是洞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就覺得可能爬得上來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡農？你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是雅各布之火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖經裡提到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死者的靈魂會變成火 引導在夜海中彷徨的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死去的人們的…火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像盂蘭盆會的燈籠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 火往海裡漂過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那團火把我帶到這裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:21:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來…那是…一個人的靈魂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道為什麼 我就是知道那是翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說 她明明只是個素未謀面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.77,0:21:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是翔子把你帶到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…翔子嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要走了嗎 道生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道生…哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和其他的火一起 往海那邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.59,0:21:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道每一團火都是誰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.59,0:21:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我全都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.72,0:22:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些是戰死的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.02,0:22:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊是我已經毀滅的故鄉的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 船前頭的火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.21,0:22:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是誰的？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.47,0:22:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…是我的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.79,0:22:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想讓人看到這麼荒涼的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.56,0:22:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 卡農你…很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.37,0:22:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都記得 那些死去的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.31,0:22:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才能夠不迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.84,0:22:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些日子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.87,0:23:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人死去是家常便飯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.10,0:23:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我努力說服自己不去在意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.77,0:23:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人會死 自己會死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.13,0:23:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些事都不去在意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.57,0:23:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 大家都活著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.02,0:23:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活在我的心裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.92,0:23:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是籠罩在一團霧裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.61,0:23:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 大家都在水的那一邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水的…那一邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.88,0:23:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡有一片風平浪靜的地方對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所在的地方 一直都是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.31,0:24:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有起伏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.03,0:24:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.67,0:24:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.40,0:24:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…你的心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.88,0:24:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.98,0:24:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被霧籠罩的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.60,0:24:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會是因為想要保護在那裡的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.91,0:24:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霧在…保護…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.36,0:24:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.90,0:24:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霧之所以迷惑人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.62,0:24:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為要保護霧裡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.43,0:24:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.94,0:24:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.77,0:25:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.97,0:25:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.30,0:25:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些我都是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.84,0:25:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.98,0:25:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡農 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.93,0:25:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福者沒有 而我們有的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.42,0:25:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.50,0:25:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是為了確認這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.77,0:25:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才想要來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.44,0:25:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來到 我自己的心裡
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,04
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.18,0:26:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是近藤家
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.12,0:26:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要老師
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.79,0:26:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.35,0:26:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是到處都找不到我媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.75,0:26:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡 要老師明明也為了咲良的事那麼操勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.34,0:26:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去Alvis…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.23,0:26:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會 我…沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.61,0:26:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這裡…是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.17,0:26:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.31,0:27:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要一直待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.35,0:27:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為媽媽可能會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.09,0:27:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我沒去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.82,0:27:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍司
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.26,0:27:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.91,0:27:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是有幾句話要跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.08,0:27:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡農…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.80,0:28:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前都沒覺得奇怪過
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.69,0:28:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到我居然只能這樣死死抓著
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.95,0:28:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來這麼爬著山 就能覺得像是在爸爸背上一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.52,0:28:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種不拚命撐著身體就可能會掉下去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.76,0:28:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.79,0:28:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.61,0:29:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 已經不在了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.66,0:29:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.42,0:29:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.05,0:29:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.03,0:29:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不行的 你身體都那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.09,0:29:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.38,0:29:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.19,0:29:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 最後一點我想自己爬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.33,0:29:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最…後？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.62,0:29:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.93,0:29:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.19,0:30:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你是來對我發火的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.61,0:30:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.38,0:30:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是來嘲笑我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.04,0:30:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.03,0:30:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你媽媽的事…真的很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.06,0:30:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.88,0:30:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得我在想 她說不定會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.42,0:30:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍司…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.86,0:30:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明得保護媽媽才行的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.36,0:30:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…媽媽…卻說要保護我…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.69,0:31:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的媽媽…也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.42,0:31:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她為了保護我而死了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.64,0:31:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要跟我說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.85,0:31:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的機體…給我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.12,0:31:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有戰鬥的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.07,0:31:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會駕駛好的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.30,0:31:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…讓給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.05,0:31:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我的Mk.Ⅷ？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.97,0:31:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會替你一起戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.42,0:31:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就留在這裡 保護自己的家
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.20,0:31:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家…我的家麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.04,0:31:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍司…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.90,0:31:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了還不明白嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.88,0:32:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的東西都一團亂！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.77,0:32:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才不是我的家！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.00,0:32:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 你為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.45,0:32:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我不知道啊 誰會知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.89,0:32:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍司…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.61,0:32:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我沒資格說這些話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.75,0:32:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該保護這裡的 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.53,0:32:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.17,0:32:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有其他法芙娜的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.69,0:32:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在戰鬥中的位置和我相同
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.32,0:32:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記錄了和我相似的心的機體會比較易於一體化
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.69,0:33:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相似…？我和你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.07,0:33:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.98,0:33:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你沒有異議 我就去向司令申請變更機體
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.03,0:33:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢著 哪裡像了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.11,0:33:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你比我…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.34,0:33:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都想要待在浮在海上的安全的東西上
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.08,0:33:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說海…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.33,0:33:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞑想訓練時的海
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.13,0:33:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看過了你們過去的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.23,0:33:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人都是什麼東西也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.79,0:33:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你創造出了自己的容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.14,0:33:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我則是船
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.50,0:33:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.39,0:33:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去開…那部機體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.10,0:33:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你一時回答不了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.79,0:34:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就等到確定了我的適應性之後再來
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.11,0:34:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是完全不一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.35,0:34:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.77,0:34:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船是會動的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.23,0:34:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚礁…是不會想要移動的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.28,0:34:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.02,0:34:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個地方比我的船美麗多了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.02,0:34:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想看到那幅心靈風景在戰鬥中變得荒涼
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.58,0:34:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是為了咲良
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.93,0:34:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…心
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.34,0:34:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.77,0:35:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種東西 早就變成這樣了！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,05
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.42,0:35:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒有失去
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.33,0:35:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還有一些留下的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.38,0:35:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案已經漸漸接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.67,0:35:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.77,0:35:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快一點 快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.14,0:35:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.14,0:35:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要猶豫 過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.17,0:35:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要迷失 來到這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.17,0:35:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.58,0:35:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想見的人 都在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.25,0:35:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有留下任何東西
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.64,0:35:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是對自己 還是對島來說
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.25,0:36:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼活下來的人是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.30,0:36:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想破了腦袋也找不到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.24,0:36:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去的自己全都逐漸分崩離析 消失不見
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.75,0:36:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該選擇的不是是否要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.92,0:36:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是要以怎樣的心去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.52,0:36:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外 沒有第二條道路
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.46,0:36:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那時 在那個人出現之前
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.86,0:36:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警報
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.21,0:36:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.11,0:36:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決意要走
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.74,0:36:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每個人都下定了決心
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.79,0:36:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這時 那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.88,0:36:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.67,0:37:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久之前 曾一度失去的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.99,0:37:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在宏大的奔流中反覆誕生的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.59,0:37:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案從遙遠的過去開始
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.13,0:37:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歷經漫長的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.28,0:37:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到了龍宮島
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.01,0:37:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我們 又不是我們的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.80,0:37:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他們 又不是他們的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.17,0:37:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與我和龍宮島的內核成對的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.38,0:37:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁紅音意志的繼承者
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.40,0:37:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這最後關頭
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.16,0:37:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指明了最後的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.24,0:37:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望——連接我們與他們的最後的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.96,0:37:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我選擇擁有「我」這顆心的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.28,0:37:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案已經昭示
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.61,0:38:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我活在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.80,0:38:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我確實存在於這裡的最後的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.32,0:38:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.81,0:38:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲洋走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.75,0:38:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們…會保護島
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.68,0:38:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.94,0:38:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.29,0:38:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你要上哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.32,0:38:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去找爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.94,0:38:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認祝福者消失了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.94,0:38:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城乙姬一醒就叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.90,0:38:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新展開偽裝鏡面
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.62,0:38:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓島以現有速度前進
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.38,0:38:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊分析新獲得的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.60,0:38:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.22,0:38:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.97,0:39:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.74,0:39:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.78,0:39:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是紅音
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.06,0:39:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的媽媽…已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.97,0:39:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.29,0:39:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 她的心現在也還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.75,0:39:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與她希望溝通的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.41,0:39:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有我們一起活著
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.88,0:39:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是這樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.29,0:39:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.62,0:39:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼簡單的事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.66,0:39:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我卻直到這一刻才發現
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.46,0:39:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.38,0:39:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.27,0:39:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在Alvis裡待命
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.87,0:39:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見醫生現在正在分析醫學資料
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.34,0:39:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她應該會需要你們的身體資料
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.02,0:39:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了拯救你們
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.54,0:39:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.45,0:39:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.19,0:39:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.46,0:40:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.93,0:40:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎 你說過
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.69,0:40:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失去你媽媽時的心情也和你一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.51,0:40:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.05,0:40:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在可以熟練運用的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.19,0:40:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那時確實都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.44,0:40:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說消滅敵人了 就連能抵抗得像樣點的武器都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.67,0:40:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.17,0:40:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你別搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.62,0:40:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可有現在的你所沒有的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.53,0:40:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你媽媽把他託付給了我
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.76,0:40:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指…？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.81,0:40:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主要資料的分析一旦有了頭緒 就要立即開會
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.56,0:40:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去通知大家 他們也要出席
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.32,0:40:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.28,0:40:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有你 一騎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,06
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.22,0:41:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.15,0:41:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎 駕駛員要到醫務室集合
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.96,0:41:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是需要我們現在的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.98,0:41:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.03,0:41:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你走著難受 不如我背你？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.30,0:41:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.99,0:41:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都在等我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.70,0:41:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰讓我們是一夥的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.10,0:41:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要我們丟下你的話就直說
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.72,0:41:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.77,0:41:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 叔叔他怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.47,0:41:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該很震驚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.34,0:41:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了那種事 那個…你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.63,0:41:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我媽媽已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.80,0:41:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.96,0:41:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 她的心還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.73,0:41:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是 以後也是
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.71,0:41:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸和我都是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.61,0:42:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.10,0:42:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.37,0:42:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.14,0:42:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.48,0:42:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我媽媽說她會安排一下
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.50,0:42:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們能在她確認資料的時候去吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.10,0:42:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝天謝地
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.44,0:42:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我一直沒吃什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.97,0:42:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.86,0:42:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？心不在焉的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.18,0:42:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.44,0:42:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎 要怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.46,0:42:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.10,0:42:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.63,0:42:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.79,0:42:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會和大家一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.72,0:42:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以確定的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.79,0:42:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這並非一切的終結
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.15,0:42:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在前路茫茫的不安之中
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.35,0:42:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在喪失許多人的痛苦之中
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.84,0:43:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望也一定會繼續存在下去
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.79,0:43:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一心一意地相信著
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.23,0:43:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信一定有些東西是永恆的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.87,0:43:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信無論何時都一定能找到它
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.60,0:43:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信即使會無數次將它迷失
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.05,0:43:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一定能再度尋回
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.52,0:43:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們始終相信
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.22,0:43:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就意味著我們現在存在於這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.76,0:43:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那裡嗎
